Output demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 20
Set Width 1600
Set Height 980
Set Padding 24
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 40ms
Set CursorBlink false

Hide
Type "cd core"
Enter
Sleep 600ms

Type "scholardevclaw demo --spec rmsnorm --skip-validate --output-dir /tmp/sdc-demo-out"
Enter
Sleep 8s
